  6046  // Retrieve the value to be passed to a request to access the next page of results
  6047  func (resp *EvaluationPage) GetNextStart() (*string, error) {
  6048  	if core.IsNil(resp.Next) {
  6049  		return nil, nil
  6050  	}
  6051  	start, err := core.GetQueryParam(resp.Next.Href, "start")
  6052  	if err != nil || start == nil {
  6053  		return nil, err
  6054  	}
  6055  	return start, nil
  6056  }

  9912  
  9913  // Retrieve the value to be passed to a request to access the next page of results
  9914  func (resp *ReportPage) GetNextStart() (*string, error) {
  9915  	if core.IsNil(resp.Next) {
  9916  		return nil, nil
  9917  	}
  9918  	start, err := core.GetQueryParam(resp.Next.Href, "start")
  9919  	if err != nil || start == nil {
  9920  		return nil, err
  9921  	}
  9922  	return start, nil
  9923  }

 10430  // Retrieve the value to be passed to a request to access the next page of results
 10431  func (resp *ResourcePage) GetNextStart() (*string, error) {
 10432  	if core.IsNil(resp.Next) {
 10433  		return nil, nil
 10434  	}
 10435  	start, err := core.GetQueryParam(resp.Next.Href, "start")
 10436  	if err != nil || start == nil {
 10437  		return nil, err
 10438  	}
 10439  	return start, nil
 10440  }
